E-commerce Product API (Backend Capstone)
ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

The E-commerce Product API is a backend RESTful API built with Django and Django REST Framework.
It provides secure endpoints for managing products in an e-commerce platform, including authentication, product CRUD operations, search, filtering, and pagination.

This project simulates real-world backend responsibilities such as API design, authentication, authorization, and data management.

